{"tid":967443,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我懷疑我老母生左個Google","createTime":"2019-01-03T13:16:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T13:39:09.000Z","uid":57895,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b9c80cdb7d0e1edfcd751bba3d16e61dd51e0060","tid":967443,"uid":57895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T13:16:23.000Z","msg":"有咩問題都問我。<br />\n<br />\n電話壞又問 電器壞又問<br />\n法律嘢又問 佢唔舒服又問我<br />\n最痴線係條魚唔新鮮都問我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我知老人家有嘢搵屋企人問係好正常<br />\n屌 但唔洗問撚完又問 答左唔知都繼續問<br />\n唔通我專登考下你誠意先答你咩<br />\n<br />\n唔知係老母痴撚線呀 定當我係Google AI<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n定我其實係電工+律師+醫生+賣魚佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（利申：廢青）<br />\n<br />\n最後，我好想講句「你問我，不如落街問棵樹」"},{"pid":"3fea238540d1d13d394261a3c8d9ef4f904f5a77","tid":967443,"uid":167330,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T13:20:08.000Z","msg":"咁右邊係咪Siri?"},{"pid":"1b57590ffc8e3e31113530686b1d333d3ad15f98","tid":967443,"uid":13288,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T13:20:34.000Z","msg":"老母我都係想同你個衰仔溝通下講多兩句野姐"},{"pid":"8ee2227d1a19acf7d608a8835a1bda2bd328feb7","tid":967443,"uid":68851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3fea238540d1d13d394261a3c8d9ef4f904f5a77","tid":967443,"uid":167330,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T13:20:08.000Z","msg":"咁右邊係咪Siri?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T13:21:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6093f70cca4cc00cbb58ca3155a2761605d7ebe4","tid":967443,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T13:21:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好想一路屌你一路問你野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable